Subject: [PATCH 4/4] UPSTREAM:DP:ath12k: add soc_dp stats for null, eapol
 and mcast pkts

Currently no stats are available to check for eapol, null
 frame and multicast pkts transmitted or received.

Hence, changes are done to add pkt count for eapol, null frame
and multicast in soc_dp_stats.

